Generated Lyrics:
Love brings joy. Joy is everywhere. Everywhere I look, I see love. Love brings joy. Joy is everywhere.
Extending the Project
Here are some ideas to enhance the project:

Character-Level Markov Chain :
Instead of splitting by words, split by characters to generate text at a finer level.
Larger Corpus :
Use a large dataset of text (e.g., books, articles, or song lyrics) to train the Markov Chain.
GUI Interface :
Add a graphical interface using libraries like tkinter for user interaction.
Save Generated Text :
Save the generated text to a file for later use.
Advanced Features :
Experiment with higher-order Markov Chains (e.g., predict based on the last two words instead of one).
